FBIS3-52592 "drnes004_n_94004" FBIS-NES-94-004 Document Type:Daily Report 6 Jan 1994 LEBANON Israelis Shell Iqlim al-Tuffah Hills in South NC0501182194 Beirut Voice of Lebanon in Arabic 1715 GMT 5 Jan 94 NC0501182194 Beirut Voice of Lebanon Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] Israeli forces stationed in al-Zaffatah shelled the Iqlim al-Tuffah hills this morning. The shelling covered Mlita, al-Luwayzah, and Jabal Safi. This afternoon, the Israeli forces in the al-Tuhrah position raked the woods around the post with mortars and machine guns.
